images.description: PanSTARRS image of region near lenticular galaxy IC 1850, often but probably misidentified as NGC 1111, and just as likely to be (or not be) NGC 1109; also shown is IC 1852, which is often but probably misidentified as NGC 1109 and/or NGC 1112
